Package nist.main

Class JsonProcessorBean

java.lang.Object
nist.main.JsonProcessorBean
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
@Named("jsonProcessorBean") @ViewScoped public class JsonProcessorBean extends Object implements Serializable
JSF backing bean that handles uploading, processing, and exporting JSON vulnerability data. It supports filtering based on years and keywords and exports results as CSV and ZIP files.
Version:
1.0
Author:
Carlos
